dct_description_sm: With a legend of points of interest. With a map of the Bassin d'Arcachon region on reverse. Includes information on sports, entertainment, and outdoor excursions. Some sites depicted pictorially. "'Perle de la côte d'argent.' Station touristique climatique et balneaire." "Tous droits de reproduction réservés."
